ActQalipu Mi'kmaq First Nation Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Qalipu Mi’kmaq First Nation Band Order
PrecisOrder Amending the QALIPU MI'KMAQ FIRST NATION BAND ORDER in order to recognize eight eligible Qalipu Mi'kmaq First Nation founding members who are entitled to be registered as Status Indians and are identified on the list of founding members provided by the Enrolment Committee to the Federation of Newfoundland Indians and to the Government of Canada on February 14, 2023.
